text: It looks good on you, that costume.

It really does...
Well, if Fuyu wears it, there isn't a costume that doesn't look good.

──Hey,
When you said that, do you mean, more than anyone else?

Everyone in this production has a matching costume right?
So I'm asking, does it suit Fuyu more than anyone else.

You're Fuyu's producer, but also everyone's producer, right?
You'd better think this through carefully, right?

I wonder what the correct response could be.
...Fufu,  alright now, would youplease give me your answer?
